animeDescription:
Lolita Anime was made on base of manga by Aki Uchiyama.

Lolita Anime Vol.1 : Uchiyama Aki no Obyoki Aki-chan
Lolita Anime Vol.2 : Milk Nomi Ningyo
Lolita Anime Vol.3 : Uchiyama Aki no Omorashi Gokko

Note: There is another series titled "Lolita Anime." but it was made a little bit earlier.
